      <section id="about">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Petal &amp; Hearth began as a small studio with a simple idea: flowers bring people together. Founded by two florists who met while styling a friend's wedding, we grew from weekend markets to a full-service shop that serves our neighborhood with daily deliveries, event design, and floral education.</p>
        <p>We prioritize seasonal sourcing, fair partnerships with growers, and low-waste design practices. Our work balances garden-inspired abundance with clean, modern lines — we like arrangements that feel intimate and lived-in rather than overly sculpted. Most importantly, we listen: every order starts with a short conversation so the bouquet suits the person and the occasion.</p>
      </section>

