        <h2>Shop: Bouquets, Arrangements &amp; Gifts</h2>
        <p>Everything in our shop is designed and arranged by our team the same day as delivery or pickup (when possible). Browse categories below; each product page lists size options and care instructions.</p>

        <div class="two">
          <div>
            <h3>Everyday Bouquets</h3>
            <p>Bright, unfussy bouquets perfect for celebrations, thank-yous, or to brighten a room. Available in three sizes:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Small</strong> — 6–9 stems, ideal for desks or bedside tables.</li>
              <li><strong>Medium</strong> — 12–16 stems, our most popular option for gifting.</li>
              <li><strong>Large</strong> — 20+ stems for impactful, statement bouquets.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3>Signature Collections</h3>
            <p>Curated seasonal palettes that reflect what’s at peak right now — soft pastels in early spring, sun-soaked tones in summer, rich jewel hues in autumn, and warm, cozy combinations in winter. These change frequently to keep your gifts fresh and surprising.</p>
          </div>
