          <li><strong>Sympathy Arrangements:</strong> Wreaths, sprays, and sympathy bouquets created with care and respect.</li>
          <li><strong>Subscriptions:</strong> Weekly, biweekly, or monthly deliveries of seasonal bouquets for home or office.</li>
